#. (itstool) path: sect3/title
#: C/index.docbook:5194
msgid "Configuring Custom LS_COLORS"
msgstr "Таңдаулы LS_COLORS баптау"

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:5195
msgid "GNOME Commander does not differentiate files types by default."
msgstr "GNOME Commander әдетте файл түрлерін ажыратпайды."

#. (itstool) path: sect3/para
#: C/index.docbook:5196
msgid ""
"You can configure it to differentiate file types like LS_COLORS does when using "
"the command shell. For more information on this you can look up the <ulink "
